OL,5, Discounted energy bills for millions of
OL,6, vulnerable people are being considered 
OL,7, as a long-term option to tackle        
OL,8, unaffordable prices.                   
OL,10,FUnder so-called social tariffs, certain
OL,11,Fgroups of people on low incomes would  
OL,12,Fbe offered lower-cost deals.           
OL,14,FJonathan Brearley, boss of the energy  
OL,15,Fregulator Ofgem, said they were a good 
OL,16,Foption being discussed with ministers. 
OL,18,FThe regulator will also investigate    
OL,19,Fsuppliers that are forcibly switching  
OL,20,Fpeople onto prepayment meters.         
